D。\", \"parameters\": {\"type\": \"object\", \"properties\": {\"name\": {\"type\": \"string\", \"description\": \"in=path | 地标名称，如 西二旗站、国贸\"}}, \"additionalProperties\": false, \"required\": [\"name\"]}}}, {\"type\": \"function\", \"function\": {\"name\": \"search_landmarks\", \"description\": \"GET /api/landmarks/search | 关键词模糊搜索地标 | 关键词模糊搜索地标，q 必填。支持 category、district 同时筛选，多条件取交集。不需 X-User-ID。\", \"parameters\": {\"type\": \"object\", \"properties\": {\"q\": {\"type\": \"string\", \"description\": \"in=query | 搜索关键词，必填\"}, \"category\": {\"type\": \"string\", \"description\": \"in=query | 可选，限定类别：subway/company/landmark\"}, \"district\": {\"type\": \"string\", \"description\": \"in=query | 可选，限定行政区，如 海淀、朝阳\"}}, \"additionalProperties\": false, \"required\": [\"q\"]}}}, {\"type\": \"function\", \"function\": {\"name\": \"get_landmark_by_id\", \"description\": \"GET /api/landmarks/{id} | 按地标 id 查询地标详情 | 按地标 id 查询地标详情。不需 X-User-ID。\", \"parameters\": {\"type\": \"object\", \"properties\": {\"id\": {\"type\": \"string\", \"description\": \"in=path | 地标 ID，如 SS_001、LM_002\"}}, \"additionalProperties\": false, \"required\": [\"id\"]}}}, {\"type\": \"function\", \"function\": {\"name\": \"get_landmark_stats\", \"description\": \"GET /api/landmarks/stats | 获取地标统计信息 | 获取地标统计信息（总数、按类别分布等）。不需 X-User-ID。\", \"parameters\": {\"type\": \"object\", \"properties\": {}, \"additionalProperties\": false}}}, {\"type\": \"function\", \"function\": {\"name\": \"get_house_by_id\", \"description\": \"GET /api/houses/{house_id} | 根据房源 ID 获取详情 | 根据房源 ID 获取单套房源详情。无 query 参数，仅路径带 house_id，返回一条（安居客），便于智能体解析。调用时请求头必带 X-User-ID。\", \"parameters\": {\"type\": \"object\", \"properties\": {\"house_id\": {\"type\": \"string\", \"description\": \"in=path | 房源 ID，如 HF_2001\"}}, \"additionalProperties\": false, \"required\": [\"house_id\"]}}}, {\"type\": \"function\", \"function\": {\"name\": \"get_house_listings\", \"description\": \"GET /api/houses/listings/{house_id} | 根据房源 ID 获取各平台挂牌记录 | 根据房源 ID 获